        %a{"data-role" => "button", :href => "/mobile/docs/buttons"} Button
      %h2 Assigning theme swatches
      %p
        Buttons can be manually assigned any of the button color swatches from the theme to add visual contrast with the container they sit inside by adding the
        %code data-theme
        attribute on the button markup and specifying a swatch letter.
      %pre
